OL,3,CWork to fix burst sewage pipe in
OL,4,CExmouth due to start
OL,6,FSouth West Water has said it's due to
OL,7,Fstart work on a "permanent solution"
OL,8,Fto fix a burst sewer in Exmouth.
OL,10,FIt follows several sewage spills over
OL,11,Fthe summer which meant the beach had
OL,12,Fto be closed to swimmers.
OL,14,FThe company said the leak was traced
OL,15,Fto a pipe on private land near Maer
OL,16,FLane wastewater treatment works in
OL,17,FAugust.
