OL,3,CWork to fix burst sewage pipe in
OL,4,CExmouth due to start
OL,6,FA number of residents and businesses
OL,7,Fhave said they are considering taking
OL,8,Flegal action against South West Water
OL,9,Fover the incident.
OL,11,FSouth West Water said the first phase
OL,12,Fof work to replace the burst section
OL,13,Fof sewer will begin later this month,
OL,14,Fand is due to be completed before the
OL,15,Fend of the year.
OL,17,FThe second phase of work will involve
OL,18,Freplacing the sewer down to Maer Road
OL,19,Fpumping station, the company added.
