OL,3,CWork to fix burst sewage pipe in
OL,4,CExmouth due to start
OL,6,FRichard Price, South West Water's
OL,7,FManaging Director for Wastewater
OL,8,FServices, said: "In my last update I
OL,9,Fsaid we were working to finalise a
OL,10,Fpermanent solution to the burst sewer
OL,11,Fwe had in Exmouth in August, so we
OL,12,Fcould give people the confidence that
OL,13,Fthey rightly expect in our operations.
OL,15,F"I am pleased to say we now have a
OL,16,Fsolution and we will be starting the
OL,17,Ffirst of two phases of work this
OL,18,Fmonth."
