OL,6,FSouth West Water said it is also
OL,7,Fworking to bring forward planned
OL,8,Fimprovements in Exmouth, including
OL,9,Fupgrading pumping stations and
OL,10,Ftreatment works to reduce the number
OL,11,Fof spills.
OL,13,FMr Price added: "As part of this work
OL,14,Fwe are already making upgrades at Maer
OL,15,FRoad pumping station and to the
OL,16,Foutfall from Maer Lane Wastewater
OL,17,FTreatment Works, both of which we aim
OL,18,Fto complete by March 2025.
